'''Muur''' was a [[yeast]]-based [[Foodstuff/Legends|food]] that was a staple of the [[Yuuzhan Vong]]. Even though it was widely used, it had an unenjoyable taste.

Prior to the [[Yuuzhan Vong War]], Yuuzhan Vong scouts planted large quanities of muur and [[lambent]]s on the planet [[Shramar]], to support the upcoming invasion.

